The paper proposes a deep learning-based method for speckle reduction in OCT images, which involves image processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves signal processing and information theory, which suggests cs.IT (Information Theory). Additionally, the paper uses deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
